<h4><span><tt>Grifter, <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Dealer</span>.</tt></span></h4>
<h4><span><tt>Soldier, Holder,</tt></span></h4>
<h4><span><tt><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Carrier,</span> THIEF.</tt></span></h4>
